{"tid":445074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"意大利兩大區公投通過爭取更大自治權","createTime":"2017-10-23T04:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-23T05:43:34.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cd46deaa5f9762467a81b97033b7e961381b0534","tid":445074,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】意大利北部兩個大區舉行無約束力公投，大比數通過爭取更大自治權。<br />\n<br />\n初步點票結果顯示，倫巴第大區約九成五選民支持爭取更大自治權，投票率超過四成。威尼托大區同樣以大比數通過公投，投票率更超過六成。<br />\n<br />\n兩個大區主席都希望藉公投結果增加與中央政府談判的籌碼，在稅務、保安、移民等範疇爭取更大自主權。他們將會與地區官員會面，確認要向中央提出的訴求。<br />\n<br />\n倫巴第和威尼托都是意大利較富庶的區域，生產總值佔全國約三成。今次公投被視為明年國會大選的風向標。擁有兩個大區控制權的北方聯盟右翼政黨五星運動及意大利力量黨，早前呼籲選民支持通過公投，執政民主黨則促請選民棄權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=240433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D240433&d=%2BWG9322KYsAL9bkPqjBoJwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=a7f5d2e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D240433&h=6a17e1ad\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=240433</a>"},{"pid":"5b66399cdb4f48404913590c141b4fa2011574da","tid":445074,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:02:18.000Z","msg":"所以歐盟先咁驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以支那先咁驚香港獨立要狂放從敗主義撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"831cf6d05c4bb91af36de93f10a30be71c22762a","tid":445074,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"世界革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab004df85e84e7aa3547e87c92ad9a09bbfaaaf5","tid":445074,"uid":628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:41:16.000Z","msg":"富遮地區全面獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b29cf2460f6cff5853d112cb5c527de8d282d8","tid":445074,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>富遮地區全面獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n庶"}]}